tailed.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2024) 0aDisaster reliefxPolitical aspectszCaribbean AreaxHistoryy19th century. 0aDisaster reliefzCaribbean AreaxHistoryy19th century. 4amanchesterhive variable pricing textbooks. 7aHISTORY / Caribbean & West Indies / General.2bisacsh  aBritish Caribbean.  aPoor Law.  adeforestation.  adisaster relief.  adisasters.  aemancipation.  aplantations.  aresilience.  aslavery.  avulnerability.1 aWebber, Oscar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertManchester University Press 2023 eBook-Packagez9783111206455oZDB-23-MUP40uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/978152616040940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781526160409423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781526160409/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-MUPb2023